org.araneaframework
Interface OutputData

All Superinterfaces:
Extendable, Narrowable
All Known Subinterfaces:
HttpOutputData
All Known Implementing Classes:
StandardServletOutputData
public interface OutputData
extends Extendable, Narrowable

A map of attributes with a scope. As OutputData is passed to different methods of BaseApplicationComponent and derivates, the scope helps the components understand where they are located in the greater hirearchy.
